    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Absolutely correct! The coin shows inertia by remaining at rest while the cardboard moves away. It's a fantastic demonstration of inertia in action."
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Alright, on to the next one!"
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Which statement is true about inertia? A) It applies only to moving objects B) All objects have inertia C) Inertia is only for heavy objects D) Inertia can be ignored"
